  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>You awaken amidst a sea of scrap, without memories. Fight to survive. Explore a treacherous wasteland. Discover who you are now.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Exsys is an action-packed adventure that blends classic 90s beat-'em-up gameplay with modern Action RPG elements. Explore a stunning 3D world of scrap and danger.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Feature</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Free Combo system:</strong> <br>Break free from rigid combos! Unleash devastating combos with free-flowing combat. Chain attacks and commands to create your own unique fighting style.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116350/extras/7f09777ef8a3ccf35527d5fd8757aa80.poster.avif?t=1736216163\" width=800 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116350/extras/7f09777ef8a3ccf35527d5fd8757aa80.webm?t=1736216163\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116350/extras/7f09777ef8a3ccf35527d5fd8757aa80.mp4?t=1736216163\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Active Skill System:</strong> <br>Discover skills in the form of equipable items. Mix and match to tailor your combat style. Use fighting game-style commands to unleash their power.  <br>Mix, match, and order a skill with the same command to create a chain of moves that execute in order.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116350/extras/e112c75424f560ff4aea185c017f20bb.poster.avif?t=1736216163\" width=800 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116350/extras/e112c75424f560ff4aea185c017f20bb.webm?t=1736216163\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116350/extras/e112c75424f560ff4aea185c017f20bb.mp4?t=1736216163\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Item system: </strong>Collect and utilize a variety of items to buff your stats, debuff enemies, and unleash special attacks. Equip up to 4 items in your quick slots for easy access during combat. Combine items and skills to create a unique fighting style and survive the harsh world of scrap.   <br><strong>Store items in the stash for your next character.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116350/extras/f5c99d76fd13b4c7a39f3a2b8416db1d.poster.avif?t=1736216163\" width=800 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116350/extras/f5c99d76fd13b4c7a39f3a2b8416db1d.webm?t=1736216163\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116350/extras/f5c99d76fd13b4c7a39f3a2b8416db1d.mp4?t=1736216163\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>\tYour character lives only once. If your character dies, you lose everything on that character and start the new game with a new character.  <br>   </strong></p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>You awaken amidst a sea of scrap, without memories. Fight to survive. Explore a treacherous wasteland. Discover who you are now.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Exsys is an action-packed adventure that blends classic 90s beat-'em-up gameplay with modern Action RPG elements. Explore a stunning 3D world of scrap and danger.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Feature</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Free Combo system:</strong> <br>Break free from rigid combos! Unleash devastating combos with free-flowing combat. Chain attacks and commands to create your own unique fighting style.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116350/extras/7f09777ef8a3ccf35527d5fd8757aa80.poster.avif?t=1736216163\" width=800 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116350/extras/7f09777ef8a3ccf35527d5fd8757aa80.webm?t=1736216163\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116350/extras/7f09777ef8a3ccf35527d5fd8757aa80.mp4?t=1736216163\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Active Skill System:</strong> <br>Discover skills in the form of equipable items. Mix and match to tailor your combat style. Use fighting game-style commands to unleash their power.  <br>Mix, match, and order a skill with the same command to create a chain of moves that execute in order.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116350/extras/e112c75424f560ff4aea185c017f20bb.poster.avif?t=1736216163\" width=800 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116350/extras/e112c75424f560ff4aea185c017f20bb.webm?t=1736216163\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116350/extras/e112c75424f560ff4aea185c017f20bb.mp4?t=1736216163\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Item system: </strong>Collect and utilize a variety of items to buff your stats, debuff enemies, and unleash special attacks. Equip up to 4 items in your quick slots for easy access during combat. Combine items and skills to create a unique fighting style and survive the harsh world of scrap.   <br><strong>Store items in the stash for your next character.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116350/extras/f5c99d76fd13b4c7a39f3a2b8416db1d.poster.avif?t=1736216163\" width=800 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116350/extras/f5c99d76fd13b4c7a39f3a2b8416db1d.webm?t=1736216163\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116350/extras/f5c99d76fd13b4c7a39f3a2b8416db1d.mp4?t=1736216163\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>\tYour character lives only once. If your character dies, you lose everything on that character and start the new game with a new character.  <br>   </strong></p></li></ul>",
